high_descs: Move to the end of the counter to right of the microwave.
Pick up the yellow handle knife of the counter.
Turn around to your right and head over to the sink.
Slice up the potato in the sink.
Place the knife down into the sink.
Remove one slice of potato.
Turn around and go the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator and place the potato on the top shelf to the left of the tomato and close it and wait for the potato to chill and take it back out..
After you close the refrigerator turn around and head back to the counter on the right side of the microwave.
Place the potato on the counter top in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Cut a piece of potato and cool it off, place on the counter.

high_descs: Step forward to the kitchen counter.
Pick up the knife  to the right of the microwave.
Turn around, step forward , then turn left and walk to the kitchen sink.
Slice the potato in the sink  to the left of the cup.
Place the knife in front of the potato.
Pick up the center slice of potato from the sink.
Turn around, walk forward, then turn left and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge door, place the potato slice to the lower left of the tomato on the top shelf, then close the door. Wait a few seconds and take the potato out of the fridge.
Turn right, walk around the kitchen table and head to the kitchen counter.
Place the potato upright on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Chill a slice of potato in the fridge and place on the counter.

high_descs: Go forward to the counter with the microwave on top.
Pick up the yellow knife from the counter.
Turn right and go to the front of the sink.
Slice a half of the potato in the sink.
Place the yellow knife on the front edge of the sink.
Take one slice of the potato from the sink.
Turn around and go to the front of the refrigerator.
Remove the potato slice after cooling on the shelf next to the tomatoes in the refrigerator.
Turn around and go to the microwave on the left across the kitchen.
Place the potato slice on the counter on the right of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled slice of potato on the counter.
